武汉一线医护人员的除夕夜：一个人的大年三十并不孤单。
Wuhan on the eve of the first-line medical personnel: a person's New Year's Eve is not alone.
作者：高瑜静 曹学平 来源：中国经营网。
Author: Gao Yujing Cao Xueping: China Operations Network.
本报记者 高瑜静 曹学平 合肥报道农历年三十，本是阖家团圆的除夕夜，但作为首批驰援武汉市医疗救治中心（武汉市金银潭医院）的湖北省中医院护士长杨晶，却是“一个人的年夜饭，一个人的大年三十”。
This reporter Gao Xuejing Cao Xueping Hefei covered the 30th anniversary of the Chinese New Year, but as the first time to help Wuhan City Medical Treatment Center (Wuhan Gold and Silver Pool Hospital), Yang Jing, the head nurse of Hubei Chinese Hospital, is "a person's New Year's Eve.
“一个人的年夜饭，一个人的大年三十，却不曾感到孤单！因为有家人朋友的关心，更有医院领导和同事的问候与关怀！如果不是远处零星响起的鞭炮声，真忘记了今天是大年夜……却一丝一毫也不敢忘记在这场没有硝烟的战场上，白衣战士的责任与担当！愿上空的阴霾早日散去，艳阳高照的日子快快到来！到那时，磨山上依旧鸟语花香；绿道上依旧人流熙攘；站在黄鹤楼上看江面船来船往；你我的生活依旧如常……”除夕夜，杨晶在朋友圈感慨道。
"A person's dinner, a person's New Year's Eve, but did not feel lonely! Because of the care of family and friends, hospital leaders and colleagues of greeting and care!
一个人的年夜饭自1月20日新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情传播形势严峻以来，武汉市卫健委随即组织抽调护理人员增援武汉市医疗救治中心。
Since January 20, when the spread of the new coronavirus pneumonia became severe, Wuhan Health Care Commission organized the deployment of nurses to reinforce the Wuhan Medical Treatment Centre.
接到通知后，湖北省中医院医务人员纷纷主动请缨，递出了一张张申请奔赴防治一线的“请战书”。
After receiving the notification, Hubei traditional Chinese medicine hospital medical staff volunteered to hand out each application to the prevention and treatment of the frontline "invitation letter."
这些“请战书”的背后，是使命的召唤，是坚定的抉择，更是责任的力量。
Behind these "invitation letters," is the calling of the mission, is a firm choice, but also the power of responsibility.
湖北省中医院于1月22日派出包括杨晶护士长在内的8位护士驰援金银潭医院。
On January 22, the Hubei Chinese Hospital dispatched eight nurses, including the head nurse Yang Jing, to assist the gold and silver pool hospital.
湖北省中医院检验科卢振华1月22日写下请战书，要求到一线，额外排班杜月月是湖北省中医院骨科的一名普通护士，她给护士长的微信内容让人泪目。
Du Yueyue, an ordinary nurse in the orthopaedic department of Hubei Province, sent a tearful message to the head nurse.
“护士长，要支援隔离病房可以先派我去，我家里没有小孩老人需要照顾的，有时间的。
Nurse, I can be sent to the isolation ward first. There are no children in my house. There are no elderly people to look after.
”在驰援金银潭医院的同时，湖北省中医院各科室的医务人员也纷纷在院内投入到防控战斗中。
Meanwhile, medical staff from the TCM hospitals in Hubei Province have been involved in prevention and control operations in the hospital.
从患者的个人防护、物品的消毒隔离，到病人就诊和转诊流程的优化，用实际行动践行着救死扶伤的初心和使命。
From personal protection of patients, disinfection and isolation of articles, to the optimization of the patient's medical treatment and referral process, with practical actions to implement the first heart and mission of life-saving.
据湖北省中医院相关负责人称，“医院感染管理办公室的全体医务人员几乎日夜不停，很难回家。
"The staff of the Hospital Infection Management Office work almost all day and night, making it difficult to go home," said the director of Hubei traditional Chinese medicine hospital.
”湖北省中医院医务人员微信沟通截图湖北省中医院风湿病科副主任叶志勤的朋友圈1月24日是除夕，当晚在武汉市各医院的医生护士仍然坚守岗位，与病人一起度过除夕夜。
"On January 24, 2007, Chinese New Year's Eve, doctors and nurses from hospitals in Wuhan, Hubei Province, stayed on their posts and spent New Year's Eve with patients.
湖北省中医院后勤保障人员为前线医务人员送去营养补给物。
The logistics support personnel of Hubei TCM hospital deliver nutrition supplies to the front-line medical staff.
特别地，热心市民为医务人员送去了除夕夜蛋糕，更让医务人员心中涌起暖流。
In particular, warm-hearted citizens sent New Year's Eve cake to medical staff, which made them warm.
新春钟声敲响之时，无数杨晶这样的医护人员依然坚守在岗位上，守护着人民健康。
On the sound of the new spring bell, countless medical personnel such as Yang Jing still cling to their posts, guarding the health of the people.
他们是最勇敢的“逆行者”，向他们致敬！（以上图片由湖北省中医院提供）（编辑：曹学平 校对：彭玉凤）。
They are the bravest of the "inverse", salute them! (Above picture provided by Hubei Chinese Hospital) (Edited by Cao Xueping, proofread by Peng Yufeng).
